{
  "page": "Howard Pyle",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Pyle\" title=\"House Pyle\"><img alt=\"House Pyle.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/0b/House_Pyle.svg/50px-House_Pyle.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/0b/House_Pyle.svg/75px-House_Pyle.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/0b/House_Pyle.svg/100px-House_Pyle.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Ser</span><br />Howard Pyle</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Howard_Pyle\" title=\"Howard Pyle\"><img alt=\"Howard Pyle.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/08/Howard_Pyle.svg/50px-Howard_Pyle.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/08/Howard_Pyle.svg/75px-Howard_Pyle.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/08/Howard_Pyle.svg/100px-Howard_Pyle.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Ser</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Pyle\" title=\"House Pyle\">House Pyle</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Crownlands\" title=\"Crownlands\">Crownlands</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><span style=\"white-space:nowrap\">Personal arms</span></th><td>\nA grey iron greathelm on white surrounded by grey roundels</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Hedge_Knight\" title=\"The Hedge Knight\">The Hedge Knight</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table> \n<p><b>Howard Pyle</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/House_Pyle\" title=\"House Pyle\">House Pyle</a> during the reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Daeron_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Daeron II Targaryen\">Daeron II Targaryen</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Howard_Pyle&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Howard attended the <a href=\"/index.php/Ashford_Tourney\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ashford Tourney\">Ashford Tourney</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/209_AC\" title=\"209 AC\">209&#160;AC</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Behind_the_Scenes\">Behind the Scenes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Howard_Pyle&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Behind the Scenes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Ser Howard is listed on one version of <a href=\"/index.php/List_of_characters_and_arms_in_The_Hedge_Knight_graphic_novel_collection\" title=\"List of characters and arms in The Hedge Knight graphic novel collection\">the roll of arms</a> included in selected printings of the collected version of the graphic novel adaptation of <a href=\"/index.php/The_Hedge_Knight_(comics)\" title=\"The Hedge Knight (comics)\">The Hedge Knight</a>, which depicts the Pyle greathelm sigil surrounded by a bordure of grey roundels, thereby differing slightly from House Pyle's original sigil. He does not appear in the original novella. \n</p><p>The knight may be a homage by <a href=\"/index.php/George_R._R._Martin\" title=\"George R. R. Martin\">George R. R. Martin</a> to <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Howard_Pyle\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Howard Pyle\">Howard Pyle</a> , the author of <i><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Merry_Adventures_of_Robin_Hood\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:The Merry Adventures of Robin Hood\">The Merry Adventures of Robin Hood</a></i> and a writer recommended by Martin.<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Howard_Pyle&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/index.php/The_Hedge_Knight_(comics)\" title=\"The Hedge Knight (comics)\">The Hedge Knight</a> (Graphic Novel)</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/index.php/Not_A_Blog\" title=\"Not A Blog\">Not A Blog</a>: <a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://georgerrmartin.com/notablog/2013/03/13/reading-recommendations/\">Reading Recommendations</a>, March 13, 2013</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403165202\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.095 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.335 seconds\nPreprocessor visited